                        <li><a class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-transform duration-200 hover:bg-[#eef7ff] hover:translate-x-2 text-gray-800" href="/DirectorEscolar"><i class="bi bi-person-badge mr-3 text-[#0074d9]"></i><span>Directores</span></a></li>
